<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Smart Ponto</title>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <%= csp_meta_tag %>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag "tailwind", "data-turbo-track": "reload" %>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag "application", "data-turbo-track": "reload" %>
  <%= javascript_importmap_tags %>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css">
</head>

<body class="bg-background text-foreground">
  <div class="relative min-h-screen overflow-hidden bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,_rgba(248,248,252,0.98),_rgba(248,248,252,0.92))]">
    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top_left,_rgba(96,85,246,0.18),_transparent_34%),radial-gradient(circle_at_bottom_right,_rgba(122,106,247,0.12),_transparent_30%)]"></div>
    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-y-0 left-0 hidden w-1/2 bg-[linear-gradient(135deg,_rgba(255,255,255,0.92),_rgba(237,234,249,0.72))] lg:block"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10">
      <%= render "shared/flash" %>
      <main class="mx-auto flex min-h-screen w-full max-w-7xl items-center px-4 py-8 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid w-full gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.1fr)_minmax(360px,460px)] lg:items-center">
          <section class="hidden lg:block">
            <div class="max-w-xl space-y-8">
              <div class="space-y-5">
                <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 rounded-full border border-white/70 bg-white/80 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-foreground shadow-sm backdrop-blur">
                  <span class="flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary text-primary-foreground shadow-sm">
                    <i class="fas fa-clock text-sm"></i>
                  </span>
                  <span>Smart Ponto</span>
                </div>

                <div class="space-y-4">
                  <p class="text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-muted-foreground">
                    Painel institucional agil
                  </p>
                  <h1 class="max-w-lg text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-foreground xl:text-5xl">
                    Registro, aprovacao e auditoria com clareza desde a primeira tela.
                  </h1>
                  <p class="max-w-lg text-base leading-7 text-muted-foreground xl:text-lg">
                    Um fluxo direto para colaboradores, gestores e RH resolverem o ponto do dia sem atrito, com linguagem clara e estados previsiveis.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
                <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/80 bg-white/88 p-4 shadow-sm backdrop-blur">
                  <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-foreground">Agilidade</p>
                  <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-6 text-muted-foreground">Acoes principais aparecem com clareza e pouco ruido visual.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/80 bg-white/88 p-4 shadow-sm backdrop-blur">
                  <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-foreground">Transparencia</p>
                  <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-6 text-muted-foreground">Erros, pendencias e proximos passos ficam sempre explicitos.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/80 bg-white/88 p-4 shadow-sm backdrop-blur">
                  <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-foreground">Confianca</p>
                  <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-6 text-muted-foreground">Visual leve, institucional e acessivel para uso recorrente.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="w-full">
            <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-md lg:max-w-none">
              <div class="mb-6 flex items-center justify-center lg:hidden">
                <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 rounded-full border border-white/80 bg-white/88 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-foreground shadow-sm backdrop-blur">
                  <span class="flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary text-primary-foreground shadow-sm">
                    <i class="fas fa-clock text-sm"></i>
                  </span>
                  <span>Smart Ponto</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <%= yield %>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </main>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
